c: 1
v: 6
t: "dullana, warshdna, wwfqna 'iilaa altariq almstqym, wthbtna ealayh hataa nlqak, wahu al'islam, aldhy hu altariq alwadih almawsil 'iilaa ridwan allah wa'iilaa jnth, aldhy dl ealayh khatm rusulah wanbyayh muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, fala sabil 'iilaa saeadat aleabd 'iilaa balastqamt elyh"